<HL>
   Hasbro Inc. Stock Repurchase
</HL>
<DATE>
08/27/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B6A
</SO>
<CO>
   HAS
</CO>
<IN>
BUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK)
</IN>
<LP>
   PAWTUCKET, R.I. -- Hasbro Inc. said its board of directors
approved the company's purchase of up to three million of its
common shares "in the open market or otherwise."
   Hasbro said it would use some of the repurchased shares
for funding its employee stock-option plans and outstanding
warrants.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   On July 31, Hasbro had 57.9 million shares outstanding.
The shares closed Friday at $13 apiece, down from $17.325 on
Aug. 1.
</TEXT>
